Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a wondrous stage created\Nby illusory light and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the best entertainment \Nshow in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it moves and excites all who see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a girl who aspired\Nto be a part of this Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the spirit of the stage which\Ncan only be seen by the chosen ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I would like to present to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the many dramas which have\Ndeveloped at Kaleido Stage so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.72,0:01:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.63,0:02:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who came from Japan\Naspiring to be a part of Kaleido Stage:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora Naegino, 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pass today's\Naudition no matter what
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a member of Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will! I will! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came with high hopes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but awaiting her was a\Nseries of unexpected occurrences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, she cleared all those\Nhurdles with her natural willpower
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and unrivaled athletic prowess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she arrived at the Kaleido Stage\Nthat she dreamed of. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! I'm really late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank goodness! This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! My name is Sora Naegino!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the auditions ended just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I came all this way\Nfrom Japan for this audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really? Okay,\Nthen come up on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:03:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The auditions are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Layla Hamilton... It's really her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's a reason for \Nwhy I was late and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\Na stage production begins on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just go home like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely, desperately\Nwant to join Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's been my dream to \Nperform in Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Kaleido Stage that she dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was unable to audition,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her dream to appear on stage was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show is going to start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, you can stay and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about all I can do for you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she was able to watch the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My arm got twisted!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ended up injuring a cast\Nmember due to a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! What the heck are you doing here?!\N--Then, an unexpected person showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fill the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got a sudden chance to\Nappear on stage for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show started while she was\Nfull of anxiety and expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! A flip! Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't do it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't perform at all! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rabbit, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't say that I can't do it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do it right now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see below...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep smiling until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora was touched, appearing on stage\Nfor the first time as she had dreamed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand just how\Nnaïve you were now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no place for you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She'd dreamed of Kaleido Stage\Nsince she was very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was this the end of Sora's dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're passing a girl who \Ndidn't even audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, the audience\Nwill come here just to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having had her talent recognized by the boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was officially allowed\Nto join Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it was also the beginning\Nof many excruciating ordeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fateful Golden Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, everyone, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like cleaning that much,\Ncan you do our share too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora was admitted under \Nspecial circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--We want to go to our lessons early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and the other trainees \Ngave her a hard time for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--So take care of it for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Furthermore, the top star,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--I feel a little better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Layla, made an outrageous demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't mean like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you show us your Golden Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A great maneuver that only Layla could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I don't\Nacknowledge your existence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then. I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you that I can \Ndo the Golden Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'll be looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you can't do it after\Nstating so boldly that you would,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus began the hard training\Nwhich determined Sora's survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fall, make sure you\Nland on your back. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have enough\Nmomentum! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never knew just swinging \Nwould be this hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I will do it no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:40.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thus, in order to gain the muscle strength
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--During the day, she studied the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--At night, she stayed late and trained hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--to perform various tricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora's mental and physical exhaustion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:44.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--you have to eat a low-fat \Nand high-protein diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--neared their peak due \Nto this harsh schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's working really hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought you something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you haven't eaten anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:10:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's earnest attitude\Nwon her new friendships.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she managed to\Ndo all this in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can just grab the bar now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she still can't maintain\Na beautiful pose in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before she catches the bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what she's doing can't be\Ncalled the Golden Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By tomorrow... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to perfect it by tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the date that\Ndetermined Sora's fate arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see what kind of\NGolden Phoenix she'll show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do it. I need \Nto believe in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's challenge was almost reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could Sora perfect the big\Nmaneuver, the Golden Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under pressure that she had to immediately\Nwithdraw from Kaleido Stage if she failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:11:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could Sora perfect the big\Nmaneuver, the Golden Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's big once-in-a-lifetime gamble began.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The bar should not be my aim. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My aim should be my love, Romeo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, I can be Juliet. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't get the last part right,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that was definitely the Golden Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have to acknowledge you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you can stay at Kaleido Stage now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Sora became a real\Nmember of Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, she made the show successful
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Mia and Anna, who'd\Nbecome very close friends of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she kept giving hopes\Nand dreams to all kinds of people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the course of her success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lonely Rosetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The French diabolo prodigy\Nperformer is finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. She's really a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1} Shhh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Um, well, I'm your fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rosetta was a proud prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she put on a show that was nothing less\Nthan you would expect from a world champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She showed a high level \Nof performance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's amazing. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I wonder why? It's not that fun to watch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's like a well-oiled diabolo machine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I'm bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is your last performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the pay, I will pay you one\Nweek's worth as agreed in the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't need to\Nappear on stage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta's pride was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wanting to do something for her, Sora...\N--Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be able to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind bringing\NRosetta back on stage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, no! Let's hurry, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I've never done diabolo before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:14:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would Sora be able to\Nappear on stage with Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Kalos want me to pair up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should always expect\Nourselves to perform flawlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better not to do it \Nthan to make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta's words were harsh.\NBut Sora never gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, I'm going to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, on the outdoor stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch! What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you're awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm watching Sora's\Nshow, it makes me nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I'm worried she's\Ngoing to make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She does, in fact, make mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--but once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, where are you, Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--she can be incredibly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable, like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch Sora's performance today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta saw Sora's\Nperformance for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, she saw the audience's smiling\Nfaces as she had never seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely different from my show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta! You came to see my show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see what our diabolo\Nperformance might look like together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, at last, it's time for the\Nfirst diabolo battle in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world diabolo champion, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see the long-awaited\Noutcome of this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing good! Go, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winner, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The applause and cheers didn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The stage exists to entertain the audience."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them etched that important\Nfact in their minds once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your magic, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, Sora climbed up\Nanother rung towards being a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, when she performed The Little Mermaid,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she overcame all sorts of ordeals\Nwith her efforts and inborn spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she won the lead role that\Nshe had dreamed of at Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora played an important part admirably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a new Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla, who had been\Nwatching how Sora progressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,finally acknowledged her as a\Nfull-fledged performer as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:33.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora got an opportunity to perform\Non the same stage with Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whom she had aspired to be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the difference in\Ntheir skill levels was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard they tried,\Ntheir timing never matched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Layla took unexpected action.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bye, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks... Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stay here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here so I can study\Nyour rhythms and pauses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please try to learn\Nmy moves and rhythms too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your moves and rhythms...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the dining hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bowwow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, their life together suddenly started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora tried hard to adjust to Layla's pace\Neven though she was unsure of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't many days left\Nuntil the opening date of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their performance was far from perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And around this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're too close....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better if we lower\Nthe difficulty of the climax a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you want to\Nmake the climax scene easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow you to make the climax easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us tomorrow, one more day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had one more day left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this time, they took unexpected action.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to start special training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I repeat\Nthe same things like I've been doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the final product will\Nbe a safe and boring show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real fight between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A real fight with Miss Layla? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will you accept this challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then their real fight \Nwithout a lifeline began.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has such amazing spirit. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I lose my nerve even a little,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she really is going to knock me in the sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drop your guard, you'll be shark bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate that awaited the\Ntwo of them after this was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more day left until opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The intensity of their training increased,\Ncontinuing on, even through the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you reaching your limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then came the opening day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would their first \Nco-performance be a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.14,0:22:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not received this kind of\Npleasant applause for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy and I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through this co-performance with Layla,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora had grown up a lot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she had only just begun\Nwalking the path to stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this, what kind of ordeals awaited her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All kinds of hard luck flocks\Nyour way as if it's spurring you on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swept away by it, time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.62,0:23:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as predicted, take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will get you out right away {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forcibly only (Drive with the fastest speed){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view I look down at every day is the best{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
